description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gatinho purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 400, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, Leverage for East, 8 for South, and 8 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50508-26882-1.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [400 Votes, Hall of Fame]
